<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="step-vi">step <strong><em>vi</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /step/    美 /step/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>跨步；踏脚：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>step back
后退</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please <strong>step aside</strong> to make room for the passengers.
请靠边站，给乘客让地方。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A lady and her husband <strong>stepped off</strong> the train in Boston.
一位女士和她的丈夫在波士顿火车站下了车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Great things happen when you <strong>step out</strong> of your comfort zone.
当你踏出自己的自在区，好事就会发生。</p></div></div>